"Founder of FPF & FPA",slug:"nate-towers",photo:{url:oa,title:a,focalPoint:{x:b,y:b},src:oa,thumbnail:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&w=500",thumbnailLarge:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&w=800",png:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&fm=png&h=3000&w=2000",pngHd:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fm=png",jpeg:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&fm=jpg&h=1920&w=1920",jpegHd:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fm=jpg",webp:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&fm=webp&h=3000&w=2000",webpHd:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fm=webp",height:ob,width:oc,alt:a,responsiveImage:{bgColor:"#c4815f",src:"https:\u002F\u002Fwww.datocms-assets.com\u002F103914\u002F1770920309-nate.png?fit=max&h=3000&w=2000",width:c,height:od,aspectRatio:oe,alt:a,title:a,base64:"data:image\u002Fpng;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABgAAAARCAIAAABIGvtnAAACT0lEQVR42kVUC5bjIAwDm09C0r3\u002FTTsBDCtBdpaqNC\u002FBsmQ7DQ7LBznyXc7PVf7c5VPO6ziOFGJQ9d7NaWN0s9btaf1n4Vvbz9O\u002FrdXWcd\u002FGDCRyE6cBD87puANY3PlYvBf\u002FLtn338\u002Fv2kRgAddmfFmc\u002FItfZEOmVyFk7ziwzvh\\u002FJ8JW2iVJvGNCWYkzrmwzKh6oNE0kmEStDIdV8b9+f6gAiajlUlQbFhIdYm8RkS+vSPzaePp1l9iTRAAqydi6jcwIeS7sVEorQV9U4iH75GX\u002FOnj2\u002FtuXbQoV64Fw4qisvaRWvYwUjgmt7Qt02kTx2ibXiwHE\u002FPR0tPi61HzCimB1WGonyy1msvL9g3SuJILmtOtTsHCbm2lJ8IsOP4lzD0LcTVf24JPnJcg0BgHnkBInXsC\u002FrjUx8xtcBgTq4SgcBAKt6nBeXa+7rgk\u002Fe7\u002FmWcmv0eEH3fDpSZ77fIX7IHRjT\u002FRoixAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC"}},video:a,bio:"\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EIf you&rsquo;re here, you likely have questions &mdash; about retirement, taxes, Social Security, or whether you&rsquo;re truly on track. We&rsquo;re glad you&rsquo;re here.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EI founded Five Pathways Financial to bring clarity, structure, and confidence to families navigating life&rsquo;s most important financial decisions. After more than 15 years in the industry, I saw how often retirement planning became product-driven and fragmented. We built this firm differently: education first, strategy second, and implementation only when it genuinely serves the client.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EAs a Chartered Retirement Planning Counselor&reg; (CRPC&reg;), my focus has centered on retirement income, tax strategy, asset positioning, and long-term coordination. Retirement isn&rsquo;t just a milestone &mdash; it&rsquo;s a structural shift that deserves thoughtful, intentional planning.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EToday, my role is to instill these principles into every advisor and guide at Five Pathways. I work closely with our team to ensure fiduciary responsibility, long-term alignment, and education-first planning are embedded in every client relationship. I trust our advisors implicitly with the goals and futures of the families we serve.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EWe embrace intelligent technology &mdash; including AI &mdash; to enhance precision and analysis, while preserving what matters most: empathy, ethical judgment, strategic thinking, and behavioral coaching during uncertain times. The future of financial guidance is the integration of advanced systems and human wisdom.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EAt its core, Five Pathways exists to reduce stress and elevate confidence. Our team is here to help you see the full picture, make informed decisions, and move forward with clarity.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E\n\u003Cp class=\"p1\"\u003EOn behalf of all of us, we look forward to serving you and helping you build a retirement plan that truly fits your life &mdash; today and for decades to come.\u003C\u002Fp\u003E",speciali